{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/yuk-kenalan-sama-si-bedil-marbot-dadakan-mesjid-al-ikhlas/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Yuk Kenalan Sama Si Bedil, Marbot Dadakan Mesjid Al-Ikhlas","content":"<p>Ada yang baru nih! Udah kenal sama <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/comic/si-bedil-mendadak-marbot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Si Bedil</a>, Marbot dadakan Mesjid Al-Ikhlas? Akhir bulan Juni kemarin CIAYO Comics kedatangan beberapa komik pendatang baru. Pastinya bulan-bulan selanjutnya juga akan ada beberapa komik baru yang nggak kalah keren.</p>\n<p>Yuk, kenalan dulu, siapa sih Si Bedil? Apa yang unik dari dia? Kita bakalan bahas satu per satu beberapa hal yang perlu Kamu tahu sebelum baca komik ini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_8101\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8101\" data-attachment-id=\"8101\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/yuk-kenalan-sama-si-bedil-marbot-dadakan-mesjid-al-ikhlas/attachment/4-43/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/4-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/4-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/4-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8101\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/4-2.jpg\" alt=\"(CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-8101\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(CIAYO Comics)</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>Bedil, Sosok Pemuda Alim Tapi Masih Keren karena Ketaatannya dalam Agama Tidak Membatasi Pergaulannya</strong></p>\n<p>Bedil adalah anak muda mandiri yang bener-bener  taat dengan aturan agama. Setiap apa yang dilakukan dalam hidupnya, tidak lepas dari aturan agama. Sebelumnya komik Si Bedil ini sangat viral di medsos karena pembahasannya yang renyah, ringan, sangat menyentuh kehidupan anak muda khususnya remaja dan mahasiswa.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_8098\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8098\" data-attachment-id=\"8098\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/yuk-kenalan-sama-si-bedil-marbot-dadakan-mesjid-al-ikhlas/attachment/3-48/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/3-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/3-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/3-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8098\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/3-2.jpg\" alt=\"(CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-8098\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(CIAYO Comics)</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>Ustadz Thor-X Meminta Bedil Buat Jadi Pengganti Aa Kim yang Ada Urusan Keluarga di Cimahi</strong></p>\n<p>Kisah Si Bedil dimulai dari panggilan dadakan oleh Ustadz Thor-X ke Mesjid Al-Ikhlas. Dia ditawari jadi marbot (penjaga mesjid) buat ngegantiin Aa Kim. Aa Kim adalah opa Korea yang jadi marbot sebelumnya, tapi dia harus pulang kampung ke Cimahi.</p>\n<p>Kesibukan Bedil di kampus membentuknya jadi sosok yang mandiri. Pengalaman menjadi marbot mesjid tentu akan menambah pengalaman dan tantangan baru bagi Bedil dalam mengatur waktu. Marbot atau penjaga mesjid itu punya tanggung jawab sukarela untuk menjalani kegiatan seperti adzan, mengurus segala kepentingan mesjid seperti kebersihan, perawatan dan lain-lain.</p>\n<p>Si Bedil akan mencoba tantangan baru dalam hidupnya. Berbagai penyesuaian, manajemen waktu, serta penentuan skala prioritas pastinya nggak akan mudah. Kalau dilihat dari sudut pandang ini, komik ini bakal menyajikan konflik-konflik batin antara diri sendiri, waktu, serta skala prioritas. Dan jelas, cerita Si Bedil bukan drama religi yang datar-datar aja.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_8095\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8095\" data-attachment-id=\"8095\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/yuk-kenalan-sama-si-bedil-marbot-dadakan-mesjid-al-ikhlas/attachment/2-1-6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-1-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-1-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-1-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8095\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"(CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-8095\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(CIAYO Comics)</p></div></p>\n<p>Kira-kira, bisa nggak ya Si Bedil menjalankan Amanat Ustadz Thor-X  buat menjaga Mesjid Al-Ikhlas sebagai marbot? Kisah Si Bedil bakal nemenin setiap <em>weekend</em> Kamu, karena selalu update setiap hari Sabtu. Biar nggak ketinggalan, Kamu bisa download aplikasi CIAYO Comics, atau kunjungin web <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CIAYO.COM</a>. Jangan lupa <em>subscribe </em>mahakarya Seto Buje sebagai pembuat cerita sekaligus ilustrator dari komik ini. Happy reading!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_8092\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8092\" data-attachment-id=\"8092\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/yuk-kenalan-sama-si-bedil-marbot-dadakan-mesjid-al-ikhlas/attachment/1-48/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/1-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/1-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/1-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8092\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/1-2.jpg\" alt=\"(CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-8092\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(CIAYO Comics)</p></div></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"4c8b58be-1359-537c-a237-bf59a09a6ec2"}}}